name: Global X Active Canadian Bond ETF
longDescription: In order to achieve its investment objective, HAD invests primarily in a portfolio of Canadian debt including debt-like securities denominated in Canadian dollars. The Sub-Advisor, Fiera Capital Corporation Fiera or the Sub-Advisor, uses research on Canadian economic conditions and their impact on interest rates to select debt including debt-like securities that, based on the Sub-Advisors view, are believed to offer superior risk adjusted returns relative to passively managed Canadian bond indices. The investment objective of HAD is to seek longterm returns primarily through maximized interest income and capital appreciation.
